        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 77–91. Simonoonops simoni, new species, male (77–85) and female (86–91). 77. Carapace, dorsal view. 78, 86. Same, anterior view. 79. Sternum, ventral view. 80. Carapace, lateral view. 81. Mouthparts, ventral view. 82. Left embolus, prolateral view. 83. Left palp, prolateral view. 84. Same, ventral view. 85. Same, retrolateral view. 87. Abdomen, lateral view. 88. Same, ventral view. 89, 90. Genitalia, ventral view. 91. Same, dorsal view." ;
